data.description: Look here, in this Palm Park community in the Town of Whittier, a nice move-in ready opportunity for those folks looking for walking distance access to the Whittier Greenway Trail or to do some Lap Swimming in a nice Olympic size pool in the nearby Palm Park Rec Center.  This neighborhood has it all.  Easy access to all levels of shopping from local strip centers for your Dry Cleaning etc., needs on up to Regional Shopping centers.  Not to mention the inimitable Uptown Whittier!  Further this 2 bedroom 1 bath dwelling is an ideal Condo Alternative as it has NO COMMON WALLS so no noisy drunks to deal with!!  The seller retired and is ready for a new adventure far far away.
